1
00:00:02,875 --> 00:00:04,749
[Previously]
I heard you took quite a tumble in your early years.

2
00:00:04,750 --> 00:00:06,041
Your cultivation has been stagnant since.

3
00:00:06,250 --> 00:00:08,041
Your fists may shatter walls,

4
00:00:08,292 --> 00:00:10,082
but they won't break the laws of our Great Sui.

5
00:00:10,417 --> 00:00:12,249
Young master, your martial realm is low,

6
00:00:12,542 --> 00:00:14,041
yet your fist intent is solid.

7
00:00:14,500 --> 00:00:15,541
Quite remarkable.

8
00:00:16,000 --> 00:00:17,791
I wonder if this return to your hometown

9
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:18,957
will ignite within you

10
00:00:18,958 --> 00:00:21,041
a heart set on slaughtering every pest?

11
00:00:21,292 --> 00:00:23,749
If the Ninth Realm cannot subdue you,

12
00:00:24,208 --> 00:00:25,999
then smash right through it.

13
00:00:26,458 --> 00:00:29,082
If the Human and Demon races ever go to war,

14
00:00:29,500 --> 00:00:30,666
I ask that Lord Bai

15
00:00:31,042 --> 00:00:32,082
review this first

16
00:00:32,583 --> 00:00:33,541
before deciding.

17
00:00:41,167 --> 00:00:41,666
Milady.

18
00:00:42,083 --> 00:00:43,374
Last year's New Year phrase was 'Jia',

19
00:00:43,625 --> 00:00:44,749
and this year it is 'Tao'.

20
00:00:44,792 --> 00:00:45,874
So, speak an idiom

21
00:00:46,000 --> 00:00:47,000
containing the word

22
00:00:47,292 --> 00:00:48,582
'Li', and you shall be rewarded.

23
00:00:51,042 --> 00:00:52,499
Peaches and plums do not speak,

24
00:00:52,708 --> 00:00:54,291
yet a path is formed beneath them.

25
00:00:57,708 --> 00:00:58,749
Lush and blooming peaches,

26
00:00:59,208 --> 00:01:00,666
peach cheeks and apricot face,

27
00:01:01,125 --> 00:01:02,374
common peaches and vulgar plums,

28
00:01:02,750 --> 00:01:03,750
to return a peach for a plum.

29
00:01:05,292 --> 00:01:06,499
To substitute one thing for another,

30
00:01:08,667 --> 00:01:09,124
Absurd!

31
00:01:09,125 --> 00:01:10,707
Utterly absurd!

32
00:01:32,833 --> 00:01:33,833
As expected...

33
00:01:34,292 --> 00:01:35,292
the moon shines brightest at home.

34
00:01:35,667 --> 00:01:36,667
Our mountains...

35
00:01:37,042 --> 00:01:38,042
are prettier than anywhere else.

36
00:01:38,792 --> 00:01:39,792
I'm back.

37
00:01:43,958 --> 00:01:45,499
Old Master takes the fool,

38
00:01:45,625 --> 00:01:48,332
back to the ancestral home!

39
00:02:25,792 --> 00:02:26,832
Was I not magnificent?

40
00:02:26,958 --> 00:02:27,624
Just standing here,

41
00:02:27,625 --> 00:02:28,957
those beasts didn't dare move!

42
00:02:34,125 --> 00:02:35,125
Wei Bo.

43
00:02:35,958 --> 00:02:36,958
Milord.

44
00:02:37,042 --> 00:02:38,082
Is someone here to cause trouble?

45
00:02:39,167 --> 00:02:39,874
Of course not.

46
00:02:39,917 --> 00:02:40,291
Wei Bo,

47
00:02:40,417 --> 00:02:41,041
what are you doing here?

48
00:02:41,125 --> 00:02:42,125
Fate brought us together.

49
00:02:42,792 --> 00:02:43,957
I moved to Mount Piyun

50
00:02:44,125 --> 00:02:44,999
to be your neighbor.

51
00:02:45,125 --> 00:02:45,666
From now on,

52
00:02:45,875 --> 00:02:47,499
please look after me.

53
00:02:48,667 --> 00:02:49,916
What about the bamboo house
you asked me to build?

54
00:02:50,125 --> 00:02:50,666
How is it coming along?

55
00:02:50,792 --> 00:02:51,792
It was finished ages ago.

56
00:02:52,458 --> 00:02:53,874
No cutting corners, I assure you.

57
00:02:54,042 --> 00:02:55,541
The view is expansive,

58
00:02:55,542 --> 00:02:57,041
and the scenery is beautiful.

59
00:02:57,042 --> 00:02:58,124
Sneaking around like a thief...

60
00:02:58,625 --> 00:02:59,999
doesn't look like a good omen.

61
00:03:04,083 --> 00:03:05,499
In the future, our Luopo Mountain

62
00:03:06,000 --> 00:03:07,041
will be quite lively.

63
00:03:09,750 --> 00:03:10,750
Luopo Mountain isn't yours.

64
00:03:11,417 --> 00:03:12,124
Right, right.

65
00:03:12,333 --> 00:03:13,624
You, Chen Ping'an, are the owner.

66
00:03:13,917 --> 00:03:14,917
I'm just a guest.

67
00:03:15,083 --> 00:03:15,666
Enough.

68
00:03:16,333 --> 00:03:17,832
Nowadays, every mountain sect in town

69
00:03:17,833 --> 00:03:19,041
is busy establishing their turf.

70
00:03:19,333 --> 00:03:21,249
I had picked a treasure spot for my house,

71
00:03:21,917 --> 00:03:22,666
but alas,

72
00:03:22,792 --> 00:03:24,791
Luopo Mountain's Earth God shrine
took it first.

73
00:03:26,667 --> 00:03:28,124
Making excuses one after another...

74
00:03:28,875 --> 00:03:30,082
I'd like to see what kind of bird

75
00:03:30,333 --> 00:03:32,332
this flashy display actually produces.

76
00:03:44,500 --> 00:03:45,500
This is my bamboo house.

77
00:03:54,042 --> 00:03:54,874
From now on, Luopo Mountain

78
00:03:54,875 --> 00:03:55,875
is half your home.

79
00:03:56,042 --> 00:03:56,582
Stay as you please.

80
00:03:56,875 --> 00:03:57,916
Changing your tune already?

81
00:03:58,208 --> 00:03:59,582
Who was it that said earlier

82
00:03:59,667 --> 00:04:01,916
Luopo Mountain wasn't ours?

83
00:04:02,458 --> 00:04:04,541
For the esteemed Earth God to argue
with me...

84
00:04:04,875 --> 00:04:05,875
is quite beneath you, isn't it?

85
00:04:23,042 --> 00:04:25,666
Could this be bamboo from the
Bamboo Sea Cave Heaven?

86
00:04:26,500 --> 00:04:28,332
Milord, you truly hide your talents.

87
00:04:30,083 --> 00:04:31,083
Milord, Milord!

88
00:04:31,292 --> 00:04:32,749
The view here is spectacular!

89
00:04:33,583 --> 00:04:34,707
Can we live here?

90
00:04:37,333 --> 00:04:39,291
I knew Chen Ping'an was no ordinary man.

91
00:04:40,083 --> 00:04:41,083
Milord,

92
00:04:41,167 --> 00:04:41,832
next, should we visit

93
00:04:42,042 --> 00:04:43,624
some specific palace or manor?

94
00:04:51,167 --> 00:04:53,416
Why are we heading straight for a grave?

95
00:04:56,583 --> 00:04:58,041
Much has happened on this journey.

96
00:04:59,083 --> 00:05:00,207
I'll tell you slowly later.

97
00:05:00,792 --> 00:05:01,874
Though you probably won't believe it...

98
00:05:03,208 --> 00:05:04,666
I actually met Gu Can's father.

99
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:06,000
Perhaps...

100
00:05:08,125 --> 00:05:09,125
Milord,

101
00:05:09,167 --> 00:05:10,749
I once read in a book

102
00:05:11,042 --> 00:05:12,332
that after people die,

103
00:05:13,042 --> 00:05:15,124
their souls might return to the
ancestral temple

104
00:05:15,708 --> 00:05:17,124
to endure via sacrifices.

105
00:05:35,750 --> 00:05:36,999
I need to stop by the blacksmith first.

106
00:05:37,750 --> 00:05:39,041
Miss Ruan is a very good friend of mine.

107
00:05:39,542 --> 00:05:40,457
When you see her later,

108
00:05:40,458 --> 00:05:41,458
address her as Sister Ruan.

109
00:05:42,042 --> 00:05:42,541
Later,

110
00:05:42,958 --> 00:05:44,082
I'll give you each an extra Snake
Gallstone.

111
00:05:45,125 --> 00:05:46,125
Alright!

112
00:05:46,417 --> 00:05:48,749
I'm old enough to be her ancestor,

113
00:05:49,083 --> 00:05:50,291
why should I call her sister?

114
00:05:50,542 --> 00:05:52,249
She is Saint Ruan Qiong's daughter.

115
00:05:52,625 --> 00:05:53,625
If you wish to die,

116
00:05:53,750 --> 00:05:54,750
I won't stop you.

117
00:05:55,167 --> 00:05:56,582
Ruan Qiong?

118
00:05:56,958 --> 00:05:58,916
You mean the immortal from
Fengxue Temple?

119
00:05:59,833 --> 00:06:01,666
I will treat Sister Ruan with utmost
respect.

120
00:06:02,792 --> 00:06:04,499
I wouldn't dare embarrass Milord.

121
00:06:11,458 --> 00:06:13,416
Milord is surrounded by important
figures.

122
00:06:13,458 --> 00:06:14,957
Where is my chance to earn merit

123
00:06:14,958 --> 00:06:15,958
and claim a reward?

124
00:06:18,500 --> 00:06:19,500
Blind fool!

125
00:06:19,958 --> 00:06:21,041
How dare you provoke my lord!

126
00:06:22,292 --> 00:06:23,292
You wretched woman!

127
00:06:23,667 --> 00:06:24,582
Just because you're a water spirit,

128
00:06:24,625 --> 00:06:25,874
you think you can fight me?

129
00:06:26,667 --> 00:06:28,457
But once this old master touches water,

130
00:06:28,458 --> 00:06:30,332
I become invincible in body training!

131
00:06:36,625 --> 00:06:37,625
Got you!

132
00:06:38,042 --> 00:06:39,042
Come back.

133
00:06:40,917 --> 00:06:42,749
This woman has a slender waist
and round hips...

134
00:06:43,167 --> 00:06:44,167
Take her as a maid.

135
00:06:44,208 --> 00:06:45,208
Let go.

136
00:06:46,708 --> 00:06:48,666
I am the newly appointed River God
of Dragon Whisker River.

137
00:06:49,125 --> 00:06:50,416
I was merely patrolling

138
00:06:50,750 --> 00:06:51,999
as per my duties.

139
00:06:52,208 --> 00:06:53,208
I meant no offense.

140
00:06:53,750 --> 00:06:54,791
I beg the Immortal

141
00:06:55,167 --> 00:06:56,291
to show mercy.

142
00:06:56,500 --> 00:06:57,500
We were the ones out of line.

143
00:06:57,708 --> 00:06:58,457
My name is Chen Ping'an.

144
00:06:58,667 --> 00:06:59,667
I'm a local who just returned

145
00:06:59,792 --> 00:07:01,916
from a long journey. I didn't know
when the town built this shrine.

146
00:07:02,667 --> 00:07:03,667
May I ask, Lady River God,

147
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:05,000
where are you originally from?

148
00:07:05,458 --> 00:07:06,624
We mountain and river deities

149
00:07:06,708 --> 00:07:08,082
have severed ties with the mortal
world.

150
00:07:08,583 --> 00:07:10,166
If Young Master Chen needs anything

151
00:07:10,417 --> 00:07:11,666
in the future, just let me know

152
00:07:12,167 --> 00:07:13,291
by the river. I won't refuse.

153
00:07:14,375 --> 00:07:15,666
Don't know what's good for you, huh?

154
00:07:15,833 --> 00:07:17,457
Bullying my kind-hearted lord?

155
00:07:24,583 --> 00:07:25,874
Young Master Chen.

156
00:07:26,292 --> 00:07:27,292
Ptooey!

157
00:07:27,333 --> 00:07:29,624
A little bastard whose parents died
early.

158
00:07:30,000 --> 00:07:31,916
Why didn't you just die on your
travels?

159
00:07:31,940 --> 00:07:52,940
(Watch the Latest Donghua Episodes: www.h-donghua.xyz)

160
00:07:53,958 --> 00:07:54,958
Miss Ruan.

161
00:07:56,708 --> 00:07:57,708
You're back.

162
00:08:01,375 --> 00:08:02,624
I took the liberty of bringing back

163
00:08:02,833 --> 00:08:04,666
some chicks from your neighbor's place.

164
00:08:05,500 --> 00:08:06,541
But wild cats got to them...

165
00:08:06,958 --> 00:08:08,082
snatched away two.

166
00:08:09,667 --> 00:08:10,667
It's fine.

167
00:08:10,833 --> 00:08:11,874
My skills have improved greatly.

168
00:08:12,292 --> 00:08:13,166
I'll make soup for Miss Ruan

169
00:08:13,292 --> 00:08:13,832
later.

170
00:08:14,167 --> 00:08:15,207
No killing, no killing!

171
00:08:15,542 --> 00:08:16,624
They're very well-behaved.

172
00:08:17,125 --> 00:08:18,707
I've even given them names.

173
00:08:24,125 --> 00:08:25,791
My father took in three new disciples.

174
00:08:26,625 --> 00:08:27,249
That long-browed youth

175
00:08:27,333 --> 00:08:28,916
is a descendant of the Xie family
in town.

176
00:08:29,125 --> 00:08:30,125
Xie Ling.

177
00:08:32,583 --> 00:08:33,999
Look at your tiny chicken heart.

178
00:08:34,250 --> 00:08:35,082
No ambition at all.

179
00:08:35,208 --> 00:08:36,291
And you're any better?

180
00:08:36,542 --> 00:08:37,957
This is called hiding our strength

181
00:08:38,625 --> 00:08:39,625
You don't know squat.

182
00:08:44,500 --> 00:08:45,500
Greetings, Uncle.

183
00:08:45,708 --> 00:08:47,624
I am a maid serving Lord Chen Ping'an.

184
00:08:48,875 --> 00:08:49,832
What are you chatting about?

185
00:08:49,875 --> 00:08:51,332
So lively and cheerful.

186
00:08:51,833 --> 00:08:52,833
What are you looking at?

187
00:08:53,458 --> 00:08:54,458
I'm warning you,

188
00:08:54,958 --> 00:08:57,207
Miss Xiuxiu is my lord's sweetheart.

189
00:08:58,000 --> 00:08:59,124
You're just a blacksmith.

190
00:08:59,375 --> 00:09:00,791
If you dare have improper thoughts,

191
00:09:01,125 --> 00:09:02,874
I'll beat you half to death with one
punch.

192
00:09:03,458 --> 00:09:04,458
I'm talking to you!

193
00:09:05,083 --> 00:09:06,249
Old man, how old are you?

194
00:09:06,458 --> 00:09:07,499
Have some shame!

195
00:09:08,417 --> 00:09:09,082
Come, come,

196
00:09:09,500 --> 00:09:10,500
don't just stand there like a log.

197
00:09:10,792 --> 00:09:11,792
Let's exchange blows.

198
00:09:13,417 --> 00:09:14,417
Master Ruan.

199
00:09:18,792 --> 00:09:19,792
Saintly Master, please accept

200
00:09:19,875 --> 00:09:21,332
this lowly one's deepest kowtow.

201
00:09:25,667 --> 00:09:27,041
I'm accompanying Chen Ping'an to town.

202
00:09:27,625 --> 00:09:28,999
We're about to forge iron.

203
00:09:29,333 --> 00:09:30,333
Come help out.

204
00:09:30,667 --> 00:09:31,041
Father,

205
00:09:31,125 --> 00:09:32,207
the hour isn't right...

206
00:09:32,458 --> 00:09:33,458
I make the decisions here.

207
00:09:33,958 --> 00:09:34,958
Don't ask questions.

208
00:09:35,208 --> 00:09:36,291
I'll fetch you some wine.

209
00:09:39,292 --> 00:09:39,916
Escaping death,

210
00:09:40,083 --> 00:09:41,083
you're destined for fortune.

211
00:09:53,333 --> 00:09:54,333
Milord,

212
00:09:54,500 --> 00:09:56,624
did you forget to prepare a gift
for Miss Ruan?

213
00:09:57,042 --> 00:09:58,624
Or do you think it's too cheap?

214
00:10:01,667 --> 00:10:02,916
Unlike you, I'm thorough.

215
00:10:03,042 --> 00:10:04,042
I prepared it long ago.

216
00:10:04,500 --> 00:10:05,500
This is a Moonlight Vase.

217
00:10:05,875 --> 00:10:07,332
It gathers the essence of the sun
and moon.

218
00:10:08,417 --> 00:10:09,417
Give it to Miss Ruan,

219
00:10:09,917 --> 00:10:11,249
it will surely yield twice the result
with half the effort.

220
00:10:12,917 --> 00:10:15,749
Then, under the dreamlike moonlight...

221
00:10:15,750 --> 00:10:16,750
Dream my foot.

222
00:10:18,042 --> 00:10:19,042
Milord, wait—

223
00:10:19,417 --> 00:10:20,041
Let's go.

224
00:10:20,167 --> 00:10:20,666
Miss Ruan,

225
00:10:20,917 --> 00:10:21,917
I couldn't think of what to give you.

226
00:10:22,125 --> 00:10:23,541
There are many delicious things outside,

227
00:10:23,708 --> 00:10:24,708
but they don't last.

228
00:10:24,875 --> 00:10:26,416
So I had no choice but to make this.

229
00:10:27,333 --> 00:10:28,333
Don't dislike it.

230
00:10:30,000 --> 00:10:31,041
It's ruined.

231
00:10:39,292 --> 00:10:40,292
I like it very much.

232
00:10:48,042 --> 00:10:49,042
It hasn't changed.

233
00:10:49,875 --> 00:10:50,875
That's good.

234
00:10:52,500 --> 00:10:54,124
It would be even better if you carved

235
00:10:54,167 --> 00:10:55,707
"Chen Ping'an gifts to Ruan Xiu"

236
00:10:56,125 --> 00:10:57,125
on it.

237
00:10:58,958 --> 00:10:59,958
Cui Ci,

238
00:11:00,000 --> 00:11:02,041
Cui Minghuang sent you to be my page,

239
00:11:02,667 --> 00:11:03,999
not to laze around.

240
00:11:14,333 --> 00:11:15,333
You're here.

241
00:11:19,625 --> 00:11:20,625
Young Master.

242
00:11:22,750 --> 00:11:23,916
If it were Second Young Master,

243
00:11:24,208 --> 00:11:25,457
he would have chatted for a while

244
00:11:25,875 --> 00:11:27,499
and complimented my new hairpin,

245
00:11:27,625 --> 00:11:28,625
said it was pretty.

246
00:11:30,792 --> 00:11:31,792
Milord,

247
00:11:31,917 --> 00:11:33,207
sometimes when girls say they like
something,

248
00:11:33,458 --> 00:11:35,166
they aren't being sincere.

249
00:11:36,833 --> 00:11:38,582
It's not that the bamboo slip you gave
is inferior...

250
00:11:39,042 --> 00:11:40,042
I just...

251
00:11:40,542 --> 00:11:41,249
I just feel

252
00:11:41,458 --> 00:11:43,332
a vase suits a beauty better.

253
00:11:44,208 --> 00:11:45,791
If Miss Ruan takes those things back,

254
00:11:46,458 --> 00:11:47,749
her Master might misunderstand.

255
00:11:48,250 --> 00:11:49,457
He might think I have ulterior motives.

256
00:11:49,958 --> 00:11:50,374
What do you mean
"might think"?

257
00:11:50,375 --> 00:11:52,082
What do you mean "might think"?

258
00:11:52,333 --> 00:11:53,041
Your intentions toward Ruan Xiu

259
00:11:53,208 --> 00:11:54,957
are obviously impure!

260
00:11:55,125 --> 00:11:56,125
What nonsense are you spouting?

261
00:11:58,042 --> 00:11:59,291
Don't kill me to silence me!

262
00:11:59,750 --> 00:12:01,499
I promise to keep my mouth shut.

263
00:12:02,000 --> 00:12:03,041
I'll be tighter-lipped than Li Baoping.

264
00:12:03,417 --> 00:12:05,082
Tighter than a sealed vase.

265
00:12:05,792 --> 00:12:06,792
What happened to my Baoping?

266
00:12:06,833 --> 00:12:07,833
Is she hurt?

267
00:12:18,625 --> 00:12:20,749
My lord is Li Baoping's Junior Uncle.

268
00:12:21,500 --> 00:12:23,041
So I admire her especially.

269
00:12:23,875 --> 00:12:24,875
And who are you?

270
00:12:25,458 --> 00:12:26,666
You must be Chen Ping'an.

271
00:12:27,250 --> 00:12:28,041
I am Li Xisheng,

272
00:12:28,042 --> 00:12:29,249
Baoping's eldest brother.

273
00:12:29,917 --> 00:12:32,332
Baoping wrote letters constantly
about how kind her Junior Uncle was.

274
00:12:33,250 --> 00:12:34,291
As her brother,

275
00:12:35,042 --> 00:12:35,916
I am deeply grateful.

276
00:12:38,000 --> 00:12:39,000
Brother Li,

277
00:12:39,042 --> 00:12:40,249
these are "Mountain Crossing Carp"
for Baoping.

278
00:12:43,417 --> 00:12:46,041
I never imagined I would witness with
my own eyes

279
00:12:46,208 --> 00:12:47,541
the miraculous sights described
in ancient texts.

280
00:12:47,750 --> 00:12:48,291
Rest assured,

281
00:12:48,750 --> 00:12:49,957
I will take great care of them.

282
00:12:50,583 --> 00:12:51,583
When Baoping returns home,

283
00:12:51,792 --> 00:12:52,792
she will be overjoyed.

284
00:12:53,458 --> 00:12:54,582
I hear you like reading.

285
00:12:55,667 --> 00:12:57,082
I picked out a few books from my
collection for you.

286
00:12:57,750 --> 00:12:58,750
No rush to return them.

287
00:12:59,542 --> 00:13:00,542
Take your time reading.

288
00:13:03,625 --> 00:13:04,999
Joking is fine,

289
00:13:05,875 --> 00:13:06,875
but remember,

290
00:13:06,958 --> 00:13:08,041
loose lips sink ships.

291
00:13:08,500 --> 00:13:10,041
Every word in this world

292
00:13:10,083 --> 00:13:11,207
carries power.

293
00:13:11,875 --> 00:13:12,875
In fact,

294
00:13:13,125 --> 00:13:14,707
the Great Dao lies within them.

295
00:13:16,708 --> 00:13:17,832
Stop putting on airs!

296
00:13:18,250 --> 00:13:19,457
Always acting like a teacher.

297
00:13:19,958 --> 00:13:21,916
Why not go be a saint at the
Confucian Academy?

298
00:13:22,333 --> 00:13:24,041
So I must first pass the imperial exams,

299
00:13:24,208 --> 00:13:25,374
and climb step by step.

300
00:13:25,542 --> 00:13:27,874
As for whether I can become a Confucian
Saint in the future...

301
00:13:28,958 --> 00:13:29,958
That is too distant.

302
00:13:30,625 --> 00:13:31,625
I dare not hope for it.

303
00:13:34,833 --> 00:13:35,833
Teacher,

304
00:13:35,917 --> 00:13:37,332
then why is it that when we read,

305
00:13:37,583 --> 00:13:39,374
we suddenly fail to recognize certain
words?

306
00:13:42,250 --> 00:13:43,749
Because those words

307
00:13:44,042 --> 00:13:46,041
were secretly borrowed by a Saint.

308
00:13:46,625 --> 00:13:48,624
Teacher, if you don't know the answer,

309
00:13:48,750 --> 00:13:50,332
do not offer random explanations.

310
00:13:50,917 --> 00:13:52,249
To know what you know

311
00:13:52,417 --> 00:13:53,624
and to know what you do not know,

312
00:13:54,000 --> 00:13:55,249
that is wisdom.

313
00:13:57,292 --> 00:13:57,791
Brother Li,

314
00:13:58,042 --> 00:13:59,042
don't be angry.

315
00:13:59,125 --> 00:14:00,416
She isn't usually like this.

316
00:14:02,500 --> 00:14:03,541
This is good.

317
00:14:03,750 --> 00:14:04,916
If you have any questions in the future,

318
00:14:05,250 --> 00:14:06,250
come ask me again.

319
00:14:11,667 --> 00:14:13,207
Now that you've returned from your
journey,

320
00:14:13,500 --> 00:14:14,707
you are still Chen Ping'an.

321
00:14:15,042 --> 00:14:16,042
That is wonderful.

322
00:14:16,625 --> 00:14:18,457
I see the green hills are full of charm,

323
00:14:18,583 --> 00:14:21,041
and I suppose the hills see me the same.

324
00:14:22,875 --> 00:14:24,707
What a beautiful day.

325
00:14:28,875 --> 00:14:30,041
Did I...

326
00:14:30,083 --> 00:14:32,207
embarrass Milord just now?

327
00:14:32,625 --> 00:14:33,625
Silly Girl,

328
00:14:33,750 --> 00:14:34,874
you think too much.

329
00:14:35,375 --> 00:14:37,041
Us staying alive is already a miracle.

330
00:14:43,125 --> 00:14:44,457
Were you asking...

331
00:14:45,000 --> 00:14:48,541
if your parents could be like Gu Can's
father,

332
00:14:49,167 --> 00:14:52,166
with their souls remaining in town
after death?

333
00:14:54,958 --> 00:14:55,958
No.

334
00:14:58,542 --> 00:14:59,542
Why?

335
00:15:06,583 --> 00:15:07,749
Because...

336
00:15:08,167 --> 00:15:09,291
it is not worth it.

337
00:15:27,792 --> 00:15:31,041
Qi Jingchun painstakingly hid you away.

338
00:15:31,625 --> 00:15:33,166
What was he planning?

339
00:15:37,083 --> 00:15:38,499
This deal...

340
00:15:39,417 --> 00:15:40,832
I agree to it.

341
00:15:53,042 --> 00:15:54,374
The richer the family,

342
00:15:54,667 --> 00:15:56,332
the more they like hiding their
talents.

343
00:15:57,292 --> 00:15:59,499
Those unaware would easily be fooled.

344
00:15:59,958 --> 00:16:00,791
Isn't that right, Silly Girl?

345
00:16:03,625 --> 00:16:04,249
Steady, steady.

346
00:16:04,333 --> 00:16:05,333
Don't panic.

347
00:16:06,208 --> 00:16:08,874
Chen Ping'an must be loaded.

348
00:16:30,208 --> 00:16:31,208
Silly Girl,

349
00:16:31,833 --> 00:16:33,624
do you think I'm really foolish?

350
00:16:39,167 --> 00:16:40,167
Tell the truth.

351
00:16:40,417 --> 00:16:41,791
Am I being tricked by Chen Ping'an?

352
00:16:45,000 --> 00:16:45,624
Swallowed, swallowed...

353
00:16:46,000 --> 00:16:47,000
All swallowed.

354
00:16:47,750 --> 00:16:49,041
Forget the Eighth or Ninth Realm,

355
00:16:49,208 --> 00:16:50,541
even the Tenth Realm is possible!

356
00:16:50,833 --> 00:16:51,666
Oh, my heavens!

357
00:16:51,792 --> 00:16:53,416
Great Master!

358
00:16:58,833 --> 00:16:59,833
Yours...

359
00:17:04,333 --> 00:17:05,333
Milord,

360
00:17:06,042 --> 00:17:07,457
this is perfect.

361
00:17:09,167 --> 00:17:09,957
Milord,

362
00:17:09,958 --> 00:17:10,999
we agreed on just one

363
00:17:11,208 --> 00:17:13,791
fine Snake Gallstone for me.

364
00:17:14,167 --> 00:17:15,249
I am your lord.

365
00:17:15,958 --> 00:17:17,249
Do I need a reason to give gifts?

366
00:17:17,458 --> 00:17:18,458
Keep it safe.

367
00:17:25,667 --> 00:17:27,499
What can a mere Saint do to me?

368
00:17:27,958 --> 00:17:29,707
And I fear no small-time Junzi.

369
00:17:32,083 --> 00:17:32,541
If you have the guts,

370
00:17:32,708 --> 00:17:34,249
come punch me to death!

371
00:17:34,875 --> 00:17:35,875
Alright!

372
00:17:36,417 --> 00:17:37,207
O-O-O-

373
00:17:37,375 --> 00:17:38,166
Milord!

374
00:17:38,250 --> 00:17:38,874
Hurry, hurry,

375
00:17:38,875 --> 00:17:39,875
come quick!

376
00:17:42,125 --> 00:17:44,332
Do you know who repaired the Cao
family home?

377
00:17:45,042 --> 00:17:46,042
What about it?

378
00:17:47,042 --> 00:17:48,332
If a house is broken, shouldn't
it be fixed?

379
00:17:48,792 --> 00:17:50,249
Whether it's fixed well or not
aside...

380
00:17:51,042 --> 00:17:52,332
have you ever heard

381
00:17:52,583 --> 00:17:55,249
the saying "digging up a sacred site"?

382
00:17:56,167 --> 00:17:57,167
Truth be told,

383
00:17:57,583 --> 00:17:58,749
I, Cao Jun, possess a unique talent.

384
00:17:59,333 --> 00:18:01,082
I can sense certain precious
existences.

385
00:18:01,667 --> 00:18:02,667
For instance...

386
00:18:02,833 --> 00:18:03,957
that sword blank.

387
00:18:05,917 --> 00:18:06,917
I'll give you some time.

388
00:18:07,792 --> 00:18:09,166
You better offer a high price.

389
00:18:15,083 --> 00:18:16,332
That sword blank...

390
00:18:16,458 --> 00:18:17,832
it has quite the origin.

391
00:18:18,625 --> 00:18:19,999
If I'm not mistaken,

392
00:18:20,375 --> 00:18:22,916
isn't that the one from the Mountain
God of Sui Shan?

393
00:18:23,750 --> 00:18:24,750
So valuable?

394
00:18:25,167 --> 00:18:26,457
No wonder you won't sell it.

395
00:18:27,083 --> 00:18:28,624
Then I have no choice but to rob you.

396
00:18:41,500 --> 00:18:42,500
Brother Li,

397
00:18:43,333 --> 00:18:44,207
regarding the books I gave you,

398
00:18:44,208 --> 00:18:46,041
there are many annotations and doubts
of mine inside.

399
00:18:46,167 --> 00:18:47,332
Try not to read those parts,

400
00:18:47,917 --> 00:18:49,374
lest you misinterpret the original
meaning.

401
00:18:49,875 --> 00:18:50,875
I've taken note.

402
00:18:51,000 --> 00:18:52,000
Step back a bit further.

403
00:18:52,375 --> 00:18:53,375
Just watch.

404
00:18:57,083 --> 00:18:58,457
You can talk philosophy all you want,

405
00:18:59,542 --> 00:19:01,041
but don't draw your blade lightly.

406
00:19:01,125 --> 00:19:02,374
Yet my philosophy

407
00:19:02,958 --> 00:19:04,291
resides within this scabbard.

408
00:19:04,667 --> 00:19:05,207
Rest assured,

409
00:19:05,625 --> 00:19:06,666
when I, Cao Jun, draw my sword,

410
00:19:07,292 --> 00:19:08,582
I rarely kill.

411
00:19:08,833 --> 00:19:10,041
So you are from the Cao family.

412
00:19:10,708 --> 00:19:12,832
Your ancestor, Cao Xi, was a
generation's Sword Immortal.

413
00:19:12,833 --> 00:19:13,833
Truly formidable.

414
00:19:14,292 --> 00:19:15,332
In that case,

415
00:19:15,833 --> 00:19:16,833
I, Li Xisheng,

416
00:19:16,875 --> 00:19:18,624
would like to see how profound your
philosophy is.

417
00:19:19,042 --> 00:19:20,042
First question:

418
00:19:20,083 --> 00:19:21,624
what is your current cultivation realm?

419
00:19:24,875 --> 00:19:25,999
Between the Eighth and Ninth.

420
00:19:27,083 --> 00:19:28,041
Sword...

421
00:19:28,042 --> 00:19:29,166
Sword Cultivator...

422
00:19:29,458 --> 00:19:30,624
Eighth or Ninth Realm?

423
00:19:32,125 --> 00:19:33,999
We're finished.

424
00:19:34,875 --> 00:19:36,374
Relying on a powerful ancestor,

425
00:19:36,583 --> 00:19:37,999
yet daring to break my rules.

426
00:19:38,583 --> 00:19:39,707
You court death.

427
00:19:40,583 --> 00:19:40,999
Master,

428
00:19:41,417 --> 00:19:42,916
should we stop that Cao family member?

429
00:19:45,208 --> 00:19:46,582
Wait until he injures someone,

430
00:19:47,083 --> 00:19:48,249
then I'll beat him to death.

431
00:19:49,000 --> 00:19:50,291
That's the proper procedure.

432
00:19:50,958 --> 00:19:51,499
Master,

433
00:19:52,292 --> 00:19:53,292
how can such a villain

434
00:19:53,333 --> 00:19:54,999
become such a powerful Qi Practitioner?

435
00:19:56,708 --> 00:19:58,082
You haven't read many books,

436
00:19:58,708 --> 00:19:59,999
so don't lecture me on good and evil.

437
00:20:00,542 --> 00:20:01,124
Remember this:

438
00:20:01,625 --> 00:20:03,166
such concepts hold no weight
on the mountains.

439
00:20:10,042 --> 00:20:11,416
Frog in a well.

440
00:20:12,083 --> 00:20:13,332
You are merely Middle Fifth Realm.

441
00:20:13,833 --> 00:20:14,957
I'll suppress my realm

442
00:20:15,333 --> 00:20:17,291
so when you eventually climb out
of that well,

443
00:20:17,708 --> 00:20:18,582
you'll realize that a person like me

444
00:20:18,708 --> 00:20:19,708
deserves the title

445
00:20:19,792 --> 00:20:20,792
of "honorable."

446
00:20:24,333 --> 00:20:25,374
Getting interesting.

447
00:20:27,042 --> 00:20:27,624
Chen Ping'an,

448
00:20:28,083 --> 00:20:29,457
please step back a little further.

449
00:20:29,792 --> 00:20:31,249
Forty or fifty paces would be best.

450
00:20:32,125 --> 00:20:33,624
With a formidable foe before you,

451
00:20:34,167 --> 00:20:36,624
you still have the leisure for
idle chatter?

452
00:20:38,000 --> 00:20:39,000
Seventh Realm.

453
00:20:40,833 --> 00:20:41,499
You Li bastard!

454
00:20:41,833 --> 00:20:43,624
Since when does a Sixth Realm
Qi Practitioner

455
00:20:43,917 --> 00:20:45,749
use simple Daoist spells

456
00:20:46,125 --> 00:20:48,082
to withstand a Seventh Realm
Sword Cultivator's philosophy?

457
00:20:48,375 --> 00:20:49,375
If word gets out,

458
00:20:49,625 --> 00:20:52,374
I, Cao Jun, will be laughed at
by swordsmen across the world!

459
00:20:52,458 --> 00:20:53,999
Perhaps your philosophy

460
00:20:54,292 --> 00:20:55,666
just isn't high enough.

461
00:20:55,958 --> 00:20:56,791
Very well...

462
00:20:56,958 --> 00:20:57,958
Eighth Realm!

463
00:21:18,917 --> 00:21:20,166
A treasure like this

464
00:21:20,292 --> 00:21:21,666
is not something you should possess.

465
00:21:22,000 --> 00:21:23,000
None of your damn business.

466
00:21:26,042 --> 00:21:27,166
Impressive indeed.

467
00:21:27,500 --> 00:21:28,874
If you have any life-saving treasures,

468
00:21:29,042 --> 00:21:30,082
use them quickly.

469
00:21:30,500 --> 00:21:32,249
Otherwise, you might die without—

470
00:21:43,042 --> 00:21:44,082
That actually works?

471
00:21:47,000 --> 00:21:48,582
Are you a leaf merchant or something?

472
00:21:48,708 --> 00:21:49,708
Apologies.

473
00:21:49,792 --> 00:21:51,874
My younger sister loves collecting
such things.

474
00:21:52,708 --> 00:21:54,749
It seems your sword's philosophy
is flawed.

475
00:21:55,792 --> 00:21:56,166
Regardless,

476
00:21:56,458 --> 00:21:57,874
we should at least decide a winner.

477
00:21:58,375 --> 00:21:59,582
My friend is waiting for me.

478
00:22:02,083 --> 00:22:03,416
Then I won't hold back.

479
00:22:18,500 --> 00:22:20,416
You insignificant Sixth Realm
Qi Practitioner.

480
00:22:20,958 --> 00:22:22,249
No matter how many treasures you have,

481
00:22:22,250 --> 00:22:23,250
or how vast your powers,

482
00:22:23,458 --> 00:22:24,458
my sword

483
00:22:24,542 --> 00:22:25,124
breaks ten thousand methods.

484
00:22:25,125 --> 00:22:26,125
Breaks ten thousand methods!

485
00:22:46,375 --> 00:22:49,041
Unless you are a banished immortal
of the Three Teachings Patriarch level,

486
00:22:49,500 --> 00:22:51,332
you couldn't control so many objects
at once.

487
00:22:52,667 --> 00:22:53,667
Who exactly are you?

488
00:23:02,417 --> 00:23:03,999
You break ten thousand methods
with one sword...

489
00:23:04,042 --> 00:23:05,332
Then I shall use Spring Leaves,

490
00:23:05,333 --> 00:23:06,124
Summer Thunder,

491
00:23:06,125 --> 00:23:06,874
Autumn Wind,

492
00:23:06,875 --> 00:23:07,457
and Winter Snow

493
00:23:07,583 --> 00:23:08,583
to accumulate

494
00:23:08,708 --> 00:23:10,082
Ten Thousand and One Methods.

495
00:23:11,500 --> 00:23:12,500
So that's it.

496
00:23:13,333 --> 00:23:14,957
Using Yin-Yang divination

497
00:23:15,208 --> 00:23:16,666
to predict my attack trajectory,

498
00:23:17,042 --> 00:23:18,042
then defending with precision.

499
00:23:18,708 --> 00:23:20,332
Otherwise, with just Sixth Realm
cultivation,

500
00:23:20,625 --> 00:23:22,207
it would be impossible to control
so many objects at once.

501
00:23:22,208 --> 00:23:23,208
Impossible to control so many
simultaneously.

502
00:23:26,458 --> 00:23:28,791
Then I'll just break your Ten
Thousand and One Methods.

503
00:23:56,333 --> 00:23:57,333
Edu...

504
00:23:57,583 --> 00:23:58,999
You were given to me by Lord
Literary Sage.

505
00:23:59,417 --> 00:24:00,541
Unless I give you away myself,

506
00:24:00,792 --> 00:24:01,792
no one

507
00:24:02,000 --> 00:24:03,624
can snatch you from me.

508
00:24:11,042 --> 00:24:12,791
Cai Jinjian of Yunxia Mountain.

509
00:24:14,000 --> 00:24:15,000
Greetings, Lady Ning.

510
00:24:15,024 --> 00:24:55,624
FANSUB: H-DONGHUA™

